  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "中国统一的成就",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "854920_8_570-616",
          "range": "570-616",
          "rangeStart": 570,
          "rangeEnd": 616,
          "markText": "我们讨论问题最好的出发点是王朝循环的理论和实践，这个主题在民间传说和历史写作中是非常突出的。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1767891935,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-01-09 01:05:35",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=570&rangeEnd=616",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=570&rangeEnd=616"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_8_6650-6712",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6650-6712",
      "markText": "总地来说，我认为我们必须肯定，中国的地形本身并不有利于中央政权的崛起；相反，它的由来已久的统一是人的制度战胜地理条件的结果。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6650&rangeEnd=6712",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6650&rangeEnd=6712"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_10_6908-6938",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "6908-6938",
      "markText": "日本人提供了导致国民党衰落和中共幸存、壮大和胜利的主要形势。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6908&rangeEnd=6938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6908&rangeEnd=6938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_8_4661-4735",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4661-4735",
      "markText": "行为科学注意到：中国的国家和社会的当代的形式，是一个基本上独立的进化过程的最终产品，它可以与希腊—罗马的和犹太教—基督教的西方相比，但绝不是一样的。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4661&rangeEnd=4735",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4661&rangeEnd=4735"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_5_882-928",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "882-928",
      "markText": "研究中国社会的任何方面，如果不从中国共产党努力改造中国社会这一背景出发，那简直是毫无意义的。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=882&rangeEnd=928",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=882&rangeEnd=928"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_13_10886-10948",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "10886-10948",
      "markText": "毛泽东从高岗饶漱石的事件中显露出，他是维护领导稳定的必不可少的支柱。但这个事件的整个过程也表明了他对党的团结构成威胁的潜力。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10886&rangeEnd=10948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=10886&rangeEnd=10948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_8_11321-11367",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11321-11367",
      "markText": "就中国而言，公元前221年以前几个世纪的混乱成了以后两千年期间赞许关于统一秩序的理想的原因。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11321&rangeEnd=11367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11321&rangeEnd=11367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_9_3169-3227",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3169-3227",
      "markText": "最后，毛泽东在把马克思主义应用于中国时，不得不以穷苦的农民为其革命的基础，而不是像共产主义规定的那样以无产者为基础。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3169&rangeEnd=3227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3169&rangeEnd=3227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_8_3240-3303",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3240-3303",
      "markText": "的确，满洲人俨然以帝位的化身自居，以至中国现代的民族主义者不能把君主立宪制作为与他们一起进入20世纪的过渡政府形式而加以接受。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3240&rangeEnd=3303",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3240&rangeEnd=3303"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_9_5914-6002",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "5914-6002",
      "markText": "可是，如上所述，中国的个人以这种方式发展起来的新作用依然脱离不了非常尊重中国的文化价值及接受家教和中央权威的框架。社会的和政治上的责任竟然压倒了西方关于个人权利的学说的吸引力。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5914&rangeEnd=6002",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=5914&rangeEnd=6002"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_12_789-819",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "789-819",
      "markText": "而台湾问题则在以后三十多年中一直是国家未竟之业中的一件大事。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=789&rangeEnd=819",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=789&rangeEnd=819"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_12_3770-3841",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "3770-3841",
      "markText": "这种态度进一步在城市建立的新政权中反映出来，地下工作者在新政权中明显地只得到次要地位。权力则落到了其经历是在人民解放军和农村地区的外地人手中。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3770&rangeEnd=3841",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3770&rangeEnd=3841"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_21_2410-2508",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2410-2508",
      "markText": "最明显的是取消了美国式的文科学院和美、英大学对学生特有的通才教育。换句话说，苏联的制度旨在造就数量更少的难以使用的文科毕业生，而培养更多的经过训练就能直接参加经济建设所需要的专业技术工作的毕业生。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2410&rangeEnd=2508",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2410&rangeEnd=2508"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_34_5312-5364",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "5312-5364",
      "markText": "动员群众、社会平等、抨击官僚主义、藐视物质上的障碍——对中国革命的奠基者来说，这些办法将会再次拯救革命。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=854920&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=5312&rangeEnd=5364",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/25a32e805d0b8825aa89528?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=5312&rangeEnd=5364"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "854920_27_3623-3645",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "3623-3645",
      "markText": "周扬宣称，从此以后，文学只能赞扬，不能批评。",
      "totalCount": 153,
